'''Raouf J. Jacob''' (wavutse 1988 muri [[Siyera Lewone|Siyera]] Lewone, [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Iburengerazuba), ni umukinnyi wa firime, producer akaba n'umuyobozi wa firime<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm6200379/</ref>.  Jacob azwi cyane kubera filime nyinshi yatsindiye ibihembo muri  filime za ''[[Siyera Lewone|Siyera]] Lewone:'' ''A Culture of Silence''<ref>https://worldwidecinemaframes.com/about-raouf-j_-jacob</ref>.  Ni n'Umuyobozi Nshingwabikorwa & Rurema akaba n'uwashinze sitidiyo / filime za Worldwide Cinema Frames LLC hamwe na Global Cinema Film Festival ya Boston (GCFF) yashinze mu 2006.<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/raouf-j-jacob/m0_xsfbl?hl=en</ref><ref>https://mubi.com/cast/raouf-j-jacob</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2005, yakoze filime CRY'','' ''America'', yakoze ubushakashatsi ku byago bibabaje no gukurikira . Yakoze kandi urukurikirane ''a Blind World''<ref>https://www.wickedlocal.com/x211927758/Human-rights-film-shown-Wednesday</ref>''.'' . Uruhererekane rwasesenguye Umunyagitugu w’Abanazi [[Adolf Hitler]] ' Igisubizo cya nyuma cy’ikibazo cy’Abayahudi <ref>https://www.primevideo.com/gp/video/detail/Sierra-Leone-A-Culture-Of-Silence/0IE5I3QQPAEDZOME0JFMN1EFHO/ref=atv_nb_lcl_he_IL?language=he_IL&ie=UTF8</ref>', [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|Jenoside yo mu Rwanda yo]] mu 1994, itsembabwoko rya Darfur muri Sudani, itotezwa ry’umuryango wa Baha'i muri Irani ndetse n’ingoma y’uwahoze ari intwazangabo Pablo Escobar muri [[Kolombiya]].<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/contact/Raouf_J_Jacob/1751792</ref> 

Muri 2014, Jacob yashyize ahagaragara film documentaire '':'' ''A Culture of Silence'' Yabaye umuyobozi, umwanditsi, producer, umukinnyi wa cinemateri, umwanditsi hamwe nivanga amajwi ya firime<ref>https://www.films.com/ecTitleDetail.aspx?TitleID=94601</ref>. Iyi filime yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi, harimo Filime nziza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya New York City 2014, iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Boston 2014<ref>https://www.films.com/ecTitleDetail.aspx?TitleID=94601</ref>, ndetse n’iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Roxbury 2014. Iyi filime kandi yerekanwe ku Isoko rya Filime rya Cannes 2014 (Marché du film de Cannes), Iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Afurika rya Silicon n'ibindi!<ref>https://www.24-7pressrelease.com/press-release/396302/award-winning-documentary-feature-film-a-culture-of-silence-opens-in-boston-at-west-newton-cinema-on-friday-november-14-2014</ref>  

